title: Any plot/layout having area under non-buildable/open space reservations admeasuring up to 500 sq
clause_text: Any plot/layout having area under non-buildable/open space reservations admeasuring up to 500 sq. m shall be cleared by shifting the existing tenants from that site.
section: 17(3) Not withstanding anything contained in these Regulations Development of Reserved land falling under the various provisions of Regulation No. 33 shall be as under:

source_pdf.text_snippet: Any plot/layout having area under non-buildable/open space reservations admeasuring up to 500 sq. m shall be cleared by shifting the existing tenants from that site.
